{{Shield}}
== Overview ==
With the success of the [[Argon (Shield)|Argon]], the Argon 400 was made as an upgrade to address several weaknesses. This newer version uses an overlapping projection technique to strengthen the layer.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Argon 400 can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
